::Striker::

Striker growls. He didn't like retreating, but there was no other choice. He 
stands up, having nearly taken out DevilDuer with several shots.

Striker turns to face Zardus. "If I hear you mistreated that protoform, 
Zardus, I will come back and format your hard drive." He says threateningly 
before flying off.
